Steps for run android app in your machine

1. follow initial steps of configure react native https://reactnative.dev/docs/environment-setup

2. setup environments files, we have 4 environments file (.env, .env.qa, .env.production, .env.development, .env.staging)

3. add stuff in to env file according to environments

4. add local.properties file in android rool level

5. add Android SDK path in this file e.g. sdk.dir=/Users/kishanmakani/Library/Android/sdk

6. run android with env e.g. ENVFILE=.env npx react-native run-android --variant=DevelopmentDebug
